{"tid":1714270,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"開始有藍屍廢老吹風叫777收手讓步","createTime":"2019-11-13T00:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T00:19:30.000Z","uid":9683,"like":200,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"087f02050684dd78d76e4a365285fa87a0949b3d","tid":1714270,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:29:32.000Z","msg":"魯迅開窗論：<br />\n　　&ldquo;中國人的性情是總喜歡調和、折中的。譬如你說，這個屋子太暗，須在這裏開一個窗，大家一定不容許的。但如果你主張拆掉屋頂，他們就會來調和，願意開窗了。沒有更激烈的主張，他們總連平和的改革也不肯行。&rdquo;（魯迅）"},{"pid":"49bb5abbb59a3deb4a07505d5223d83dc8dd5e65","tid":1714270,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4c07736e74c7a719cbfa063543cdd5cb87f59b","tid":1714270,"uid":89538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:35:17.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"6aedf3dc0b94fa73139eedace1e9c71717d0cdad","tid":1714270,"uid":5178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c4c07736e74c7a719cbfa063543cdd5cb87f59b","tid":1714270,"uid":89538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:35:17.000Z","msg":"Source?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:45:15.000Z","msg":"自己落街聽啦"},{"pid":"b78491a8c96992af3b98f07738635262602c62bd","tid":1714270,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16c120dd3a7956f010a45cd5ff9808a649fdebb","tid":1714270,"uid":108757,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:52:08.000Z","msg":"香港市民︰<br />\n<br />\n抗爭五個月來，抗爭者早已將五大訴求向政府及各界表達得清清楚楚，惟林鄭政府一意孤行，將其置之不理，陷香港於水深火熱之中，種種後果乃政府一手造成。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者對香港之愛，無人能及，停罷社會，只為政府回應訴求。我等承諾，若政府答應及落實五大訴求，抗爭者將盡快及盡最大努力，將香港社會回復平靜。若政府繼續罔顧民意，我等將繼續及升級抗爭行動，直至政府答應訴求為止。我等呼籲，政府盡快放下屠刀，回頭是岸，回歸理性討論，但並非討論五大訴求能否實行，而是落實五大訴求後如何執行。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n黎明之初，花開之時<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者啟"},{"pid":"95d79a0495fc60e06cc95468096d417751336eda","tid":1714270,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:52:23.000Z","msg":"11.14 曙光行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/evpMOT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/evpMOT</a>"},{"pid":"88718d7245d9758013d6bdbda1b3eb09c0e31a6c","tid":1714270,"uid":119128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:53:03.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},{"pid":"4f6e943426f83328d5d0942713d25c23e7571c5d","tid":1714270,"uid":194968,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:55:05.000Z","msg":"收手？ 6月可以做 唔做<br />\n為左冇謂既面子 每一步要推到最差<br />\n佢地就係想香港死 越亂越好<br />\n到今時今日有權力既依然唔做野降溫<br />\n示威者只係被動一方 做主動既永遠都係政府"},{"pid":"3cf771ea5ede5665da1e22b97558c69ca942c388","tid":1714270,"uid":44454,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"6c4c07736e74c7a719cbfa063543cdd5cb87f59b","tid":1714270,"uid":89538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:35:17.000Z","msg":"Source?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:19:10.000Z","msg":"我就係藍絲， 一直以來都反對暴力， 而家我開始討厭林鄭了， 希望政府妥協， 還我一個寧靜的香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6e6e65daebfd92663bf28bb3e876ce2c254aab","tid":1714270,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01177df6000e36ce0128bc0917d49fc3f7f211d1","tid":1714270,"uid":35262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:23:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"311181085fd510fed77b4f8b854c6f6553da3307","tid":1714270,"uid":28628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:24:44.000Z","msg":"先收林鄭皮<br />\n林鄭落台應該比五大訴求<br />\n更易令人接受<br />\n更易說服藍絲支持<br />\n就係因為林鄭企得硬<br />\n有共狗撐 所以d狗先咁撚痴線<br />\n5百萬人上街 屌走林鄭"},{"pid":"4e062a99addae179cdf9578710ee86d220f14683","tid":1714270,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0